title: NATO countries gather as Ukraine war overshadows Europe; death toll rises after Russian attack on shopping mall
content:
1. NATO countries gather as Ukraine war overshadows Europe; death toll rises after Russian attack on shopping mall  CNBC
  2. Russian strike hits Kremenchuk shopping center with more than 1,000 civilians inside, Ukraine says  NBC News
  3. Russia fired rockets at Ukraine mall containing ‘more than a thousand civilians,’ Zelenskyy says  Fox News
  4. Russian airstrike hits busy shopping mall in central Ukraine, sparking fears of mass casualties  CNN
  5. Eight killed, 21 wounded in Russian missile attack on Lysychansk - local governor  Reuters.com
